ğŸ“ƒ API Endpoints

Authentication:
- POST /api/auth/login â€“ Simulated admin login

Students:
- GET /api/students â€“ List/search students
- POST /api/students â€“ Add/update student
- POST /api/students/vaccinate â€“ Mark student vaccinated
- POST /api/students/upload â€“ Upload students CSV

Drives:
- GET /api/drives/upcoming â€“ Upcoming drives
- POST /api/drives â€“ Create drive
- PUT /api/drives/:id â€“ Edit drive

Reports:
- GET /api/reports â€“ Get vaccination records
- GET /api/reports/export/csv â€“ Download CSV report

